McFadden's R2

McFadden's pseudo r-squared for the model.

blr_mcfadden_rsq(model)

Arguments

model

an object of class glm

Value

McFadden's r-squared

Examples

model <- glm(honcomp ~ female + read + science, data = hsb2,
            family = binomial(link = 'logit'))

blr_mcfadden_rsq(model)
#> [1] 0.3072023
